page.title: 05Natalie's day
page.content: I get up at 8 o'clock,dress in my school clothes which are blue and white,then I go downstairs for breakfast.I eat toast with marmite.After that I wash my face with a flannel and clean my teeth with my yellow toothbrush.I feed my fish,then I go to school.My sister takes me across the road to my friend's house.Her Dad takes us to school in his car.We have a little playtime until the bell rings at 9 o'clock.It is Wednesday so we go to church.After church we do maths.,then we go to Street swimming pool in a coach.When we come back we have our lunch,I eat sandwiches.In the afternoon we do our topic work about the Elizabethans,then we go out to play.I might play French elastic where we jump in and out of a piece of elastic. After school I may have a piano lesson or go to Brownies.
